name: NEURAL FLEURS
description: GAN poem by @sashastiles coining the term “Neural Fleurs.” (Documentation is available showing that, as of 4.26.21, the phrase has no results in Google. Nor does “neurafleur.”) This piece nods to new media’s Tech Bloom, the allure of BOTany, and NFTulipmania, and is the title of a series of GAN-translated AI flower poems.
